  "A pharmaceutical researcher is developing a new drug that blocks the enzyme converting angiotensin I to angiotensin II. A colleague asks how this would affect the feedback loop controlling blood pressure. What would be the expected outcome?": "",
  "Blood pressure would decrease because blocking angiotensin II formation reduces vasoconstriction and aldosterone-mediated sodium retention": "",
